<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Us - Tech Blog</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Newsreader:wght@400;500;700;800&family=Noto+Sans:wght@400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    /* Consistent with landing page */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Newsreader', 'Noto Sans', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      color: #0d141c;
    }

    header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e7edf4;
      padding: 12px 40px;
      background-color: #fff;
    }

    .logo-container {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 32px;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #0d141c;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-right: 36px;
    }

    nav a:last-child {
      margin-right: 0;
    }

    .search-avatar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 32px;
    }

    .search-box {
      min-width: 160px;
      height: 40px;
      display: flex;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background-color: #e7edf4;
    }

    .search-box input {
      border: none;
      outline: none;
      background-color: #e7edf4;
      padding: 0 16px;
      flex: 1;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #0d141c;
    }

    .search-box .icon {
      padding-left: 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      color: #49739c;
    }

    .avatar {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
    }

    /* About page specific content styling */
    .about-hero {
      padding: 40px 24px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .about-inner {
      max-width: 920px;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .about-content {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e7edf4;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
    }

    .about-title {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      color: #0d141c;
    }

    .about-text {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #3a3a3a;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .team-section {
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .team-title {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #0d141c;
    }

    .team-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .team-member {
      background-color: #f8fbff;
      border: 1px solid #e7edf4;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .member-avatar {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin: 0 auto 16px;
      background-color: #dbeafe;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #3d98f4;
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .member-name {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .member-role {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #64748b;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .member-bio {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #3a3a3a;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      header {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 16px;
        padding: 12px 20px;
      }
      
      .logo-container {
        width: 100%;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }
      
      nav {
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }
      
      nav a {
        margin-right: 0;
      }
      
      .search-avatar {
        width: 100%;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }
      
      .about-content {
        padding: 24px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="logo-container">
      <div class="logo">
        <div style="width: 16px; height: 16px;">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M39.5563 34.1455V13.8546..." fill="currentColor"></path>
            <path d="M10.4485 13.8519C10.4749 13.9271..." fill="currentColor"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0;">Tech Blog</h2>
      </div>
      <nav>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/blog">Articles</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
   
  </header>

  <div class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <div class="about-content">
        <h1 class="about-title">About Our Blog</h1>
        <p class="about-text">
          Welcome to Tech Blog, your premier destination for cutting-edge technology insights, 
          in-depth tutorials, and the latest news about the digital world. Founded in 2023, 
          we're committed to delivering high-quality content that empowers our readers to 
          navigate the rapidly evolving tech landscape.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          Our team of passionate writers, developers, and tech enthusiasts brings together 
          decades of industry experience to provide you with accurate, engaging, and 
          actionable content. Whether you're a seasoned professional or just starting your 
          tech journey, you'll find valuable resources here.
        </p>

        <div class="team-section">
          <h2 class="team-title">Meet Our Team</h2>
          <div class="team-grid">
            <div class="team-member">
              <div class="member-avatar">JD</div>
              <h3 class="member-name">John Doe</h3>
              <p class="member-role">Founder & Editor-in-Chief</p>
              <p class="member-bio">
                10+ years in tech journalism. Former lead developer at TechCorp. 
                Passionate about making complex topics accessible.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member">
              <div class="member-avatar">AS</div>
              <h3 class="member-name">Alice Smith</h3>
              <p class="member-role">Senior Writer</p>
              <p class="member-bio">
                Specializes in AI and machine learning. Holds a PhD in Computer Science 
                from Stanford University.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member">
              <div class="member-avatar">RJ</div>
              <h3 class="member-name">Robert Johnson</h3>
              <p class="member-role">Web Technologies Expert</p>
              <p class="member-bio">
                Full-stack developer with expertise in modern JavaScript frameworks. 
                Creator of several popular open-source projects.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>